name: Unidentified Food Obliterator
description:
Fly around as a ufo in a farm pen to destroy the food items and gain a point, you have a limited amount of time and need to destroy as many as you can in the time limit. each level you get less time and more food items spawn, your goal is to destroy as many as you can and rack up the largest score you can. But look out for those golden melons as those are worth BIG points

Also don't forget to follow our twitter where we will post updates on our future games: https://twitter.com/ExtinguishedGa2
